all\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; font-size:x-small\">&#65279;</span></span></span></span></span>Then\r\n it is transparent.</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; font-size:x-small\">Just want to share in case someone face the same situation.</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; font-size:x-small\"><span style=\"font-family:Consolas; font-size:x-small\"></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n",
